title_bed_bats_review: Hotel in Cox's Bazar · 1 bedroom · 2 beds · 1 private bath
listing_description: Enjoy easy access to popular tourist attractions, Sugondha sea Beach and restaurants from this charming place to stay in Cox's Bazar. This is a 1 Bed Room & 1 drawing room apartment. Popular Sugondha beach is only 400 meters away. Our boutique hotel is located at Kolatoli Road from where you can enjoy direct sea view from our hotel. You'll enjoy your time at this cheerful getaway.

title_bed_bats_review: Boutique hotel in Cox's Bazar · 2 bedrooms · 2 beds · 1 private bath
listing_description: You won’t want to leave this charming, one-of-a-kind place in Cox's Bazar, ideal for 4 persons group or family with a complimentary breakfast. Our place is just adjacent to the Sugondha Sea Beach of Cox's Bazar, only a 5 min walking distance. Enjoy the World's largest unbroken sandy sea beach, the largest marine drive in the world and Buddhist monastery, and many more in Cox's Bazar.
